data.description: FOR SALE OR RENT ($2200/month)- Coronado Oaks subdivision. Custom built on a view lot and in a highly sought-out neighborhood. Featuring Hardwood floors. Plantation Shutters. Solid oak with beveled glass double door entry. Granite tops. Custom cabinets. Upgraded fixtures and built-ins. Kitchen with Stainless steel appliances, microwave, Stove, Dishwasher , Refrigerator, commercial grade stove and GE Profile Stainless steel Range Hood. Granite countertops, pantry. Breakfast bar. Recess lighting. Surround sound. All bathrooms reflecting latest designs and updates on the market, including a master with Exquisite hand-carved accents with a warm patina finish vanities for him and her, separate shower with upgraded nickel finish glass shower door and stand-alone tub. Chair railing. Crown molding. Latest closet organizers and built-ins. Garage with built-in cabinets, shelves, work area and carpeted floors and over head storage . Bay window with seating and storage below. Four bedrooms. Four bathrooms. Formal Living with huge view windows. Stunning views from main level. Formal dining. Spacious family room with fireplace. Breakfast area.. Indoor utility room with overhead cabinets. Balcony overlooking breathtaking view of mountains. French doors. Updated baths. Skylight. Walk-in closets. Energy star electronic water heaters. Professional landscaping with sprinkler system, Flagstone, Flower beds and covered patio. Gazebo with electric power, fan and outdoor Fire place.
